WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:47.000
This certificate is designed to unlock a skill set you already possess as clinicians. We'll treat this program as a personal and professional quest — an adaptation of the classic Hero's Journey. Course 1, which you're starting now, is 'Sparking Innovation: From Insight to Opportunity,' where you'll learn to see your daily clinical world differently. Course 2 is 'Building the Solution: Design, Plan, and Pitch.' And finally, Course 3 is 'Driving Impact: From Project to Lasting Change,' where you bring your vision to life. By the end of this journey, you won't just have new knowledge — you'll have a tangible playbook, and the foundation for an executive one-pager to make your ideas a reality.
